    },
    "billing_flow": [
      "1. Single supplier purchases energy in day-ahead market based on aggregated forecasts from actual meter data",
      "2. Single supplier adjusts position in intra-day market based on updated forecasts",
      "3. NO energy community settlement (no REC)",
      "4. Actual consumption/generation measured at individual meters",
      "5. Single supplier handles all imbalances in balancing market",
      "6. Single supplier bills all customers based on retail prices for net consumption",
      "7. Prosumers receive feed-in tariff for net exports to grid"
